Changes in Version 0.4
======================
* can run either erosion or erosion+transport
* enable isostatic adjustment
* erosion/transport optionally modifies ice bed
* lots of updates to documentation

Changes in Version 0.2
======================
* enabled erosion transport
* choice between various transport schemes:
  - semi-Lagrangian using interpolation
  - semi-Lagrangian using finite volumes
  - conservation of 2nd moments

Changes in Version 0.1
======================
* we've got a version and we use the GNU autotools
